===Interjection===
'''bingo!'''

# Used by players of bingo to claim a win.
# (''colloquial'') Used when finding what one has been looking for or trying to recall.
# (''colloquial'') Similarly, used to declare "You've just made my point!" or "My point exactly!".

====Synonyms====
*(''used by players of bingo to claim a win''): [[house]]!
*(''when finding something'') [[aha]]!, [[eureka]]!, [[got it]]!, [[that's it]]!, [[yes]]!

